Usage
*****

                          Mailstat [options]

@{b}-h@{ub}
@{b}--help@{ub}
     Print out the online help page

@{b}-g@{ub}
@{b}--general@{ub}
     Analyse the AmigaSmail logfile for a general analyse.

@{b}-s@{ub}
@{b}--sent@{ub}
     Analyse the AmigaSmail logfile for the sent mails.

@{b}-r@{ub}
@{b}--received@{ub}
     Analyse the AmigaSmail logfile for the received mails.  Mailstat
     generate the two kinds of analyses:

        Ę List all mail receivers

        Ę List for all sender, which mail to your site

@{b}-a@{ub}
@{b}--all@{ub}
     Analyse the AmigaSmail logfile for a overall analyse.

@{b}-n@{ub}
@{b}--no-attributes@{ub}
     Don't print any escape characters

@{b}-f date@{ub}
@{b}--from-date@{ub}
     Start analyse from date

@{b}-t date@{ub}
@{b}--to-date@{ub}
     Stop analyse at date


